### ================================================================
### STEP 4: Get User Profile
### ================================================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ================================================================
### STEP 5: Refresh Access Token
### ================================================================
# @name refreshToken
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh-token
Content-Type: application/json

